            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hm..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Leon, what's wrong? Is there something on my face...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "You... Really like wandering around here a lot, don't you?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I was wondering this for a while, but... What kind of work do you normally do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I hadn't told you? I'm an alchemist."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "An alchemist...? I've heard about them before... But what exactly do you do?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Um... I gather materials, and put them in a cauldron, and stir it around, and make things!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x25,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "...I'm sorry, I don't understand at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... How can I explain it better..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I know. Maybe you can come over to my place sometime?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Your place?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. It's a lot faster to understand alchemy by looking, rather than trying to explain it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I see, that makes sense. I'm kind of interested too... I'll come over some time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'll be waiting!"
        }
    ]
